title: Scruples (1980)
description:
1980's TV Movie taken from book of same name by Judith Krantz.

Armed with beauty, passion and ambition, an extraordinary woman enters - and conquers - a glittering realm of unimaginable wealth, jetset glamour and expensive sins.  Billy Ikehorn caters to society's high fashion fantasies at Scruples, Beverly Hills' most opulent boutique.  But sinister figures from Billy's golden present and scarlet past threaten her dazzling empire.

Cast: Lindsay Wagner, Barry Bostwick, Marie-France Pisier, Kim Cattrall, Gavin MacLeod

3 episodes - 700MB
